映式。 （普雷斯利·安/FilmMagic 摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Jason-Momoa-and-Amber-Heard-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Jason-Momoa-and-Amber-Heard-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Jason-Momoa-and-Amber-Heard-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Jason-Momoa-and-Amber-Heard-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Jason-Momoa-and-Amber-Heard-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Jason-Momoa-and-Amber-Heard-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/amber-heard">艾梅柏·希尔德</a>的治疗文件显示，这位女演员声称她的搭档<a href="/artists/jason-momoa">杰森·莫玛</a>在《<em>海王 2》</em>片场喝醉了酒，打扮得像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-depp">约翰尼·德普</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/aquaman-stars-jason-momoa-patrick-wilson-director-james-wan-superman-sea-2419227" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《海王》</em> ——由杰森·莫玛和帕特里克·威尔逊主演，以及导演詹姆斯·万主演的《海洋超人》</a></strong></li></ul><p>这些指控来自赫德的治疗师道恩休斯博士最近公布的文件，这些文件被用作去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depps-defamation-case-against-amber-heard-is-going-ahead-3022188">赫德和她的前夫约翰尼德普之间备受瞩目的诽谤审判</a>的一部分。这些文件是在德普的粉丝支付法庭费用后获得的。</p><p>希尔德在 2021 年的治疗期间就提出了这些指控。 “杰森说他希望解雇我。杰森喝醉了——片场很晚。穿得像约翰尼。也有所有的戒指。”这位女演员在笔记中写道，她声称莫玛穿得像她的前夫，是为了与她玩心理游戏。 （每个<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/aquaman-2-jason-momoa-drunk-claims-amber-heard-cut-scenes-elon-musk-letter-1235747775/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>品种</em></a>） </p><figure id="attachment_3512606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512606" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512606" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting.jpg" alt="2018 年 12 月 3 日，艾梅柏·希尔德和杰森·莫玛在纽约 Build Studio 与 Build 系列讨论《海王》。 （罗伊·罗克林/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-sitting-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512606" class="wp-caption-text"> 2018 年 12 月 3 日，艾梅柏·希尔德和杰森·莫玛在纽约 Build Studio 与 Build Series 讨论《海王》。 （罗伊·罗克林/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方，她告诉休斯，莫玛据称喝醉了出现在片场，并声称他故意试图让她从电影中被解雇。</p><p> DC的一位发言人反驳了这位女演员的说法和指控，并表示：“杰森·莫玛在<em>《海王</em>与<em>失落的王国》</em>片场始终表现得非常专业。” An insider who worked on the London set in 2021 added (per <a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/aquaman-2-jason-momoa-drunk-claims-amber-heard-cut-scenes-elon-musk-letter-1235747775/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> ): “Jason works his ass off, likes to have a beer once in a while like everyone, but doesn&#39;t show up drunk to set,” and added the co-stars joked around on set and got along. They also said that Momoa&#39;s fashion sense was always bohemian.”</p><p> <em>NME</em> has reached out to representatives of Momoa for comment.</p><p> The actress first appeared in the role of Mera — the love interest of the title character, played by Momoa — in the original 2018 film. Her role in the upcoming sequel was thrown into question in recent months though, following the lawsuit.</p><p> The case – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depp-amber-heard-jury-reaches-verdict-3238472">which was won by Depp last year</a> – saw the <em>Pirates Of The Caribbean</em> actor awarded $10million (£8million) in compensatory damages and $5million (£4million) in punitive damages after he sued Heard for defamation.</p><p> Her role in the sequel <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-are-divided-after-confirmation-that-amber-heard-is-returning-to-aquaman-3435944">left many fans with polarising opinions</a> .</p><p> Heard openly stated that the defamation trial led to her nearly being kicked off the upcoming film. “I fought really hard to stay in the movie — they didn&#39;t want to include me,” she said at the time (via <a href="https://www.unilad.com/film-and-tv/amber-heard-confirmed-to-be-returning-as-mera-in-aquaman-2-209662-20230425" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>UniLad</em></a> ). </p><figure id="attachment_3512607" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512607" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512607" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview.jpg" alt="Amber Heard and Jason Momoa attend SiriusXM&#39;s Town Hall With The Cast Of &#39;Aquaman&#39; on December 4, 2018 in New York City. （辛迪·奥德/盖蒂图片社为 SiriusXM 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Amber-Heard-and-Jason-Momoa-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512607" class="wp-caption-text"> Amber Heard and Jason Momoa attend SiriusXM&#39;s Town Hall With The Cast Of &#39;Aquaman&#39; on December 4, 2018 in New York City. (Photo by Cindy Ord/Getty Images for SiriusXM)</figcaption></figure><p> “I was given a script. And then given new versions of the script that had taken away scenes that had action in it, that depicted my character,” she continued. “They basically took a bunch out of my role. They just removed a bunch.”</p><p> Additionally, rumours about her role in the film were heightened when an online campaign launched, petitioning for her to be removed from the upcoming movie entirely. Titled “Remove Amber Heard from <em>Aquaman 2</em> ”, the petition was made on <a href="https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Change.Org</a> , and received 4.6million signatures from people wanting the sequel to find a new actress to play Mera.</p><p> In other news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/amber-heard-spent-two-months-making-an-overwatch-cosplay-for-elon-musk-3497420">it was claimed that Heard spent two months making an &#39;Overwatch&#39; cosplay for Elon Musk</a> .</p><p> Musk and Heard dated in 2016 and 2017, however, Walter Isaacson&#39;s biography of the SpaceX CEO corroborates the claim that he had pursued her since 2012.</p><p> “[Musk] told her that she reminded him of Mercy, his favourite character in […] Overwatch, so she spent two months designing and commissioning a head-to-toe costume so she could role-play for him,” Isaacson wrote.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/amber-heard-claimed-co-star-jason-momoa-turned-up-drunk-and-dressed-like-johnny-depp-to-aquaman-2-set-3512586">Amber Heard claimed co-star Jason Momoa turned up drunk and dressed like Johnny Depp to &#39;Aquaman 2&#39; set</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
